I hope you enjoy editing here and being a [[Wiktionary:Wiktionarians|Wiktionarian]]! By the way, you can sign your name on Talk (discussion) and vote pages using four tildes, like this: &#126;&#126;&#126;&#126;, which automatically produces your name and the current date. If you have any questions, see the [[Wiktionary:Help|help pages]], add a question to the [[WT:BP|beer parlour]] or ask me on my Talk page. Again, welcome! [[User:Kipmaster|Kipmaster]] 13:25, 3 May 2006 (UTC)